title: Engineer's Life at GitHub: Practical tips of nailing interviews
description: A collaborative discussion thing with The App Club - we chat about tech career options and real interview processes and tips nailing them.
body:
A collaborative discussion thing with The App Club - we chat about tech career options and real interview processes and tips nailing them. "What are the career options after a computer science degree or without a degree? How to get into those big big big tech companies? What's good/bad about them?" are the questions we need answers. Let's spend a night put this in our discussion space, and let's talk about this.

[Ticket](https://appclub-career-github.eventbrite.com)    [Recording](https://www.facebook.com/AppClubUM/videos/589778395095905/)
